description:
* Based on shounen supernatural comedy manga by http://anidb.net/cr38180 [Asou Shuuichi].
http://anidb.net/ch81960 [Saiki Kusuo] is a typical 16-year-old high school student... except he has psychic powers. He can use them to get whatever he wants, but he also knows everything that people are thinking. Everything. No surprises, no secrets, no normal human experiences. He`s kept his powers in check since childhood, but with the temptations of high school now on his mind, he`s bending the rules - and spoons.
Source: Funimation
